      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. it's just hard to balance it all cuz if i raise wages i might have to raise my prices, which might drive customers away. but if i dont, i cant afford staff. looks like there isn't really a \"right\" answer here, is there? it sounds like it just depends on which study you look at or what side you're on.",
